<li><a href="https://www.mayoclinic.org/biographies/price-katharine-a-m-d/bio-20054955"><strong><em>Katharine Price, M.D.</em></strong></a><strong><em>, Oncology, Mayo Clinic, Rochester, Minnesota</em></strong></li>
</ul>
